**Course Overview:**
The world of cartography goes far beyond traditional choropleth maps. While they are informative, there are numerous innovative ways to represent spatial data, such as dot maps, cartograms, and more. Our course takes you on a journey through the art of map making with R and ggplot2, covering preliminary data processing and visualization methods to create these diverse and engaging maps.

